{"id": 3026, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得自己生活中遇到最多的“无聊”是哪种状态？", "description": "“无聊”不是一种很容易归纳的状态，但这并不代表它完全没有规律可循。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 7300, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191009014516UbIrDkYJ21MhzPWv.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-10T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5961, "title": "你觉得自己生活中遇到最多的“无聊”是哪种状态？", "content": "你觉得自己生活中遇到最多的“无聊”是哪种状态？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 348055, "content": "无事可做型：因为闲着/当下没有目标而带来的无价值感", "image": "img/option/option/20191008230211BcmW0liXKZ9SLoqI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348062, "content": "无人关注型：因为没有人看到，感觉做啥都没有用", "image": "img/option/option/20191009003942UuTwyWBeVY5xit1c.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348064, "content": "重复体验型：反复执行/经历同样的事，熟练到失去兴趣", "image": "img/option/option/20191009004246RsoWvZuh0iHGyXw6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348065, "content": "缓解焦虑型：用小无聊（比如刷视频）转移更大的焦虑", "image": "img/option/option/20191009004857RxgIuSyzXVWBojNh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348066, "content": "错失恐惧型：害怕错过新信息，最终注意力枯竭而疲劳", "image": "img/option/option/20191009005826rhHzAE9apX8YGMul.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348067, "content": "目标迷茫型：需求都是被植入的，反而搞不清到底要啥", "image": "img/option/option/20191009010739uHtvnM0eiKsqDJdE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348068, "content": "缺乏挑战型：搜索引擎可以回答一切，只能过二手人生", "image": "img/option/option/20191009011631QCzepRan7kmDNV0b.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348069, "content": "积极废人型：看似在努力，其实内心并不相信努力有用", "image": "img/option/option/20191009014246SUmZ1Dvx2L9zAo0u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348070, "content": "都不是，我不属于以上任何一类", "image": "img/option/option/20191009014637Pf4lr7CYVFdG2mgE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}